<title>USA: Boeing to increase employee trust shares.</title>
<headline>Boeing to increase employee trust shares.</headline>
<dateline>SEATTLE 1996-11-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Boeing Co Friday said its board of directors approved an increase in the employee ShareValue Program trust fund by 1.7 million shares of Boeing stock, once the acquisition of Rockwell International Corp's aerospace and defense business has been completed.</p>
<p>In a statement, Boeing said the move represents an increase of approximately 15 percent in the shares in the trust fund, bringing the total to 13 million shares.</p>
<p>Approximately 21,000 Rockwell employees will become Boeing employees in the merger.</p>
